                                                                                              NIST SP 800-213A                                             GUIDANCE FOR THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT
                                                                                                                                                  IOT DEVICE CYBERSECURITY REQUIREMENT CATALOG

                                                                                                    3. Establish communications to provide the IoT device customers with the details
                                                                                                       necessary to establish and modify IoT device data integrity controls. Information that
                                                                                                       may be necessary to provide include details and actions such as:
                                                                                                           a. Providing IoT device customers with the details necessary to support secure
                                                                                                               implementation of the IoT device and associated systems data integrity
                                                                                                               controls.
                                                                                                           b. Providing IoT device customers with documentation describing the data
                                                                                                               integrity controls built into the IoT device and how to use them. If there are no
                                                                                                               data integrity controls built into the IoT device, include documentation
                                                                                                               explaining to IoT device customers the ways to achieve IoT device data
